short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically redirects to the new interface of Google Books. This extension is not an official product.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
